{"tid":122993,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"個市開始有小小出貨現象, 要小心","createTime":"2017-02-16T13:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T00:35:35.000Z","uid":34286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ac48be89f2263c47ea1c13b559ae382fbc639c","tid":122993,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i32.photobucket.com/albums/d23/Wilsonng1/ewewewew_zps2lpio3qh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi32.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fd23%2FWilsonng1%2Fewewewew_zps2lpio3qh.jpg&h=7c74e689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回望15年這張圖, 看看成交是怎樣變化的<br />\n一開始上升時, 價量齊升(高成交)<br />\n然後在高位派貨(高成交)<br />\n急插, 入熊市(高成交)<br />\n<br />\n連續2天, 已經過千億<br />\n但其實留意整體市況<br />\n無可否認, 有些個股或板塊繼續熱炒, 但有為數不小, 升市下倒跌(派貨?). 整體市況只能說麻麻<br />\n加上大成交, 但指數升得不多<br />\n<br />\n大成交並不一定意味好. 要看各種因素的考慮<br />\n回看15年這張圖, 大戶高位橫行派貨, 是有歷史根據的. <br />\n大時代都有一幕, 大成交但不升, 是大戶的派貨的技倆. 當然也有托指數來派貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個人結論看, 已經有輕微派貨現象<br />\n要小心這個現象"},{"pid":"dd408a9d10c27790ee823f1be6a91db907bf7bd4","tid":122993,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679082012df9cfb1e71bee1eed6f0f2c633fada5","tid":122993,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"我同意。我覺得音樂就快停。"},{"pid":"4bdc46fb4e0064c4867f6136ace02a93088f977d","tid":122993,"uid":10199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"樂觀sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44425543e81ca9f2fa846da2071183bfd6d58643","tid":122993,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樂觀SIR</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7663ec5e34ae81fbbd16f3c31701f2bae4824f","tid":122993,"u